OL,3,CMum says SEND system is 'broken' as
OL,4,Cautistic son struggles at school
OL,6,FA mother from Oxford whose autistic
OL,7,Fson struggles at his mainstream
OL,8,Fsecondary school says the special
OL,9,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,10,F(SEND) system is "broken".
OL,12,FLeandra Hamblin's son Joshua, 11, has
OL,13,Fautism and ADHD.
OL,15,FHis family went to a tribunal last
OL,16,Fsummer to try to get him into a
OL,17,Fspecial school that they felt was more
OL,18,Fsuited to his needs.
