OL,3,CMum says SEND system is 'broken' as
OL,4,Cautistic son struggles at school
OL,6,FHowever, this was denied, so he
OL,7,Fstarted at a mainstream secondary
OL,8,Fschool in September.
OL,10,FMs Hamblin said: "It was very
OL,11,Fstressful, it felt like I needed to be
OL,12,Fa solicitor and learn a lot of the law.
OL,14,F"I had to get all the reports in order
OL,15,Fto try and prove why he needed this
OL,16,Fand unfortunately it was still not
OL,17,Fenough.
OL,19,F"I don't know what more they need, I
OL,20,Fthink he would really benefit from
OL,21,Fbeing in a different setting."
