OL,3,CMum says SEND system is 'broken' as
OL,4,Cautistic son struggles at school
OL,6,FJoshua is said to be struggling with
OL,7,Fthe busyness of the school and moving
OL,8,Faround from classroom to classroom and
OL,9,Fthe situation is not just affecting
OL,10,Fhim, but his whole family.
OL,12,F"We find that it's affecting us mostly
OL,13,Frather than at school because he's
OL,14,Fmasking so the aggression does come
OL,15,Fout here a lot," Ms Hamblin said.
OL,17,F"That does mean that his brothers are
OL,18,Falso a bit traumatised by the
OL,19,Fbehaviours and myself.
