OL,3,CMum says SEND system is 'broken' as
OL,4,Cautistic son struggles at school
OL,6,F"He's now also getting quite big, he
OL,7,Fmight only be 11 but he's the size of
OL,8,Fan adult and he is strong.
OL,10,F"It puts a lot of pressure on myself
OL,11,Fand my husband."
OL,13,FMs Hamblin is worried about her son's
OL,14,Ffuture because he is getting "more and
OL,15,Fmore internalised".
OL,17,FShe described the SEND system as
OL,18,F"definitely broken" and says "there
OL,19,Fneeds to be a clearer pathway for all
OL,20,Fof us to navigate".
