OL,6,FEducation and health care (EHC) plans
OL,7,Fset out the provision of SEND support
OL,8,Fa child or young person needs.
OL,10,FIn Oxfordshire, 53.7% of new EHC plans
OL,11,Fwere issued within the statutory 20-
OL,12,Fweek time limit in 2023.
OL,14,FCouncillor John Howson, Cabinet Member
OL,15,Ffor Children's Services, Oxfordshire
OL,16,FCounty Council, said: "We have
OL,17,Foverhauled our special education needs
OL,18,Fsystem in Oxfordshire in the last 12
OL,19,Fto 15 months.
