OL,6,F"We clearly need to be able to do more
OL,7,Fbut in the end it comes down to a
OL,8,Fmatter of resourcing from the
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,F"We have spent something like #80
OL,12,Fmillion more than we have been
OL,13,Fallocated by the government for the
OL,14,FSEND area and that's sitting on
OL,15,FOxfordshire County Council's balance
OL,16,Fsheet.
OL,18,F"We're not going to go bust tomorrow
OL,19,Fbut some councils might because of
OL,20,Fthis overspend. The government has got
OL,21,Fto get the funding right."
