OL,3,CMum says SEND system is 'broken' as
OL,4,Cautistic son struggles at school
OL,6,FToday, the Public Accounts Committee
OL,7,F(PAC) said too many families are
OL,8,Fstruggling to access the help their
OL,9,Fchildren with SEND "desperately need".
OL,11,FIn a report, the committee said
OL,12,Fwhether children receive support
OL,13,Fdepends too much on their postcode, or
OL,14,Fhow well families can navigate "an
OL,15,Foften chaotic and adversarial system".
OL,17,FThe PAC has called on the government
OL,18,Fto urgently take action to improve the
OL,19,Fsystem.
