OL,6,FSchools Minister Catherine McKinnell
OL,7,Fsaid: "The system we've inherited has
OL,8,Fbeen failing families with Send
OL,9,Fchildren for far too long ` this is
OL,10,Funacceptable and that's why we set out
OL,11,Four Plan for Change to ensure no child
OL,12,Fis left behind.
OL,14,F"These problems are deep-rooted and
OL,15,Fwill take time to fix but we remain
OL,16,Fsteadfast in our commitment to deliver
OL,17,Fthe change that exhausted families are
OL,18,Fcrying out for by ensuring better
OL,19,Fearlier intervention and inclusion.
